Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:10.67,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}我很抱歉 打搅了您的午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:13.72,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:16.80,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我快吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:23.02,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,警官先生 请容我问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.96,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我犯了什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:26.73,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.69,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,您当然没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.94,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,那您找对人了吗——？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.86,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,您是拉特那女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.65,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,真菌学教授
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.01,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,工作单位 印度尼西亚大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:42.74,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我们要找的正是您
Comment: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.44,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,SARS
Comment: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.81,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,每日勤喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:26.27,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,230,,拉特那女士 您可否看一看我们制好的标本？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.41,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,您可能会注意到——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.85,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,让她自己得出结论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.50,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,这是线虫草真菌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.92,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,载玻片上怎么还加了氯唑？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:04.68,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,230,,因为样本是从人体上采集到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:12.90,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,线虫草真菌不可能在人体内存活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.33,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,如果您感到不适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.84,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,就马上离开停尸间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:09.47,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,看她的左腿底下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:48.70,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,咬她的是人类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.66,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,什么时候发生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.96,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,大概30小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.13,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,在哪儿发生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:03.50,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,230,,城西边的一家面粉加工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:07.05,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,真是理想的培养基
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.62,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,后来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:16.14,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,一个正常妇女 突然出现暴力行为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.44,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,她攻击了四位同事 咬伤其中三人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:22.36,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,他们把她锁在卫生间里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:26.03,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,警察赶来后 她又试图攻击警察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.70,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,警察朝她开了枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:34.18,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,被她咬伤的那些人怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.58,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,他们被带走并进行观察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.31,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,几小时后……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:44.65,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我们不得不按照规定 采取必要措施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:48.01,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,处决了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:53.14,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,谁咬的“她”？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.83,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我们不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.60,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,所以 外面还有感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.57,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,还有其他工人失踪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.78,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,有十四人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.86,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,拉特那女士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:29.63,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我们请您来 是希望您能协助我们 防止事态恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.34,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我们需要疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.47,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,或者特效药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:52.13,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我这一生都在研究真菌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:57.35,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,请您认真听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:00.00,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,没有特效药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.52,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,也没有疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.36,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,那我们该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.16,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:27.21,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,用炸弹轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:31.38,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,轰炸这座城市……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:36.14,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,炸死所有居民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.13,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.87,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,您能派人送我回家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:06.94,Subtitle-TLOU-JAVA,,0,0,0,,我想和家人待在一起
Comment: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.85,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.94,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fs40}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.94,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我看起来像是被感染了吗？\N{\fs40}Do I look like I'm infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.29,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,把你的胳膊露出来\N{\fs40}Show us your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.51,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行啊 我的伤口没恶化 不是吗？\N{\fs40}Yeah, it's not getting any worse, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:29.77,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,如果我们现在身处外城 为什么感染者没有蜂拥而至？\N{\fs40}If we're out in the open city, why aren't we getting swarmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:30.83,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这你别操心了\N{\fs40}Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:31.98,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我已经在操心了\N{\fs40}Well, I'm gonna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.36,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,玛琳想拿这个被感染的孩子做什么？\N{\fs40}What was Marlene doing with an infected kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.98,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我没被感染\N{\fs40}I'm not infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.82,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,在我被咬之后 她发现了我\N{\fs40}She found me after I was bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:41.80,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,她没朝你开枪\N{\fs40}And she didn't shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.82,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,显而易见\N{\fs40}Clearly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.66,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,她把我关了起来 派人每天检查我的情况\N{\fs40}She locked me up and had her guys test me every day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.78,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,判断我是不是病了\N{\fs40}to see if I was getting sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.04,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,怎么检查你的？\N{\fs40}Test you how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:48.93,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我要尿尿\N{\fs40}I have to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.71,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们检查你 怎么检查？\N{\fs40}Test you, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.13,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们让我数到十 还要我伸出手\N{\fs40}They'd make me count to 10 and hold out my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.08,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,把手稳在空中\N{\fs40}and then keep it steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.54,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,但是吧 我觉得最让他们感到惊异的\N{\fs40}But, you know, I think what really impressed them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:00.17,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,是我没变成他妈的怪物\N{\fs40}was the fact that I didn't turn into a fucking monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.84,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我能走了吗？\N{\fs40}Now can I please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.51,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs40}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.27,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,去你身后的房间 随便找个角落\N{\fs40}Back there. You can find a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:15.81,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,接着\N{\fs40}And here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,撕几页下来\N{\fs40}Tear out a few pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.90,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不会有什么坏家伙在那里等着我吧\N{\fs40}There's not gonna be anything bad in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:23.86,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,就你而已\N{\fs40}Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.49,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,哦 真好笑\N{\fs40}Oh, funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.79,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你的手伤了\N{\fs40}Broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.34,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,估计是轻微骨折 很快就好\N{\fs40}Maybe a hairline. It'll heal fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.89,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他妈的一整晚她都撑过去了 乔尔\N{\fs40}She made it through the fuckin' night, Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.06,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那不重要\N{\fs40}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.69,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,她迟早会变异\N{\fs40}It's gonna happen sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.65,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,明白吗？我们离隔离墙还不算远\N{\fs40}All right? We're still close to the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:00.94,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们可以把她偷渡回隔离区\N{\fs40}We sneak her back into the QZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.69,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,再想其他的办法拿到电池\N{\fs40}We find a different way to get the battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.90,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这就是我们最好的机会了\N{\fs40}This is our best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.95,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们把她带回隔离区 总会有人注意到她的胳膊\N{\fs40}We take her back to the QZ, someone's gonna notice her arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.50,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,扫描她的伤口 然后杀了她\N{\fs40}they're gonna scan her, then they'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.21,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那也总好过由我们动手\N{\fs40}Well, better them then us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.12,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,别再说得好像这个孩子\N{\fs40}You need to stop talkin' about this kid
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.75,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,还有一线生机似的\N{\fs40}like she's got some kinda life in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:30.85,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你饿吗？\N{\fs40}You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.93,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们可以分你些吃的\N{\fs40}You can share some of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.56,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,谢了 玛琳给我带了食物\N{\fs40}Thanks. Marlene sent me with my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.16,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你吃的是鸡肉？\N{\fs40}Is that chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:56.37,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs40}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.67,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,玛琳说这是从走私贩那里弄来的\N{\fs40}Marlene said they get it from smugglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.13,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我猜不是你俩\N{\fs40}Guess not you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.03,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿！\N{\fs40}Hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:08.68,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,为什——\N{\fs40}Why--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.22,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,为什么玛琳这么看重你？\N{\fs40}why are you so important to Marlene?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:14.22,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,别撒谎 不然我们就带你回去\N{\fs40}And don't lie to me or we'll take you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.23,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你们把我带回去 那就拿不到电池了\N{\fs40}You take me back, you don't get your battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.85,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你听到我们说话了吧？\N{\fs40}You heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那你一定也听到他想要开枪毙了你\N{\fs40}Then you must've heard that he wants to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:29.45,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我以对待成年人的方式来和你说话\N{\fs40}I'm gonna talk to you like you're an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.74,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行吗？\N{\fs40}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.74,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,乔尔和我不是什么好人\N{\fs40}Joel and I aren't good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们接这个活 是为了自己\N{\fs40}We're doin' this for us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.96,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,因为 很明显 你对某些人有价值\N{\fs40}because, apparently, you're worth something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.25,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,但是 我们如果不知道你是怎么回事 就没办法弄清你的价值\N{\fs40}But we don't know what you're worth if we don't know what we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.04,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,所以 来回答我的问题\N{\fs40}So answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.43,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,她不让我告诉别人\N{\fs40}She told me not to tell anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我现在是第一次跟其他人——\N{\fs40}and now I'm telling the first people that I--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:04.27,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,在西边某个地方 有个火萤基地\N{\fs40}There's a Firefly base camp somewhere out west,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.65,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们有医生\N{\fs40}with doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.40,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,在研究解药\N{\fs40}They're working on a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.36,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我也听过这些传闻\N{\fs40}I've heard this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.28,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不管我身上发生了什么 那都是找到疫苗的关键\N{\fs40}And whatever happened to me, is the key to finding the vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:12.95,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,仅仅如此吗？\N{\fs40}That's what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:14.95,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这话我们听过不下百万次了\N{\fs40}We've heard this a million times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:18.06,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,疫苗 灵丹妙药 没一个有用的 都一个样\N{\fs40}Vaccines, miracle cures. None of it works. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.04,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,操你妈 又不是我想提的\N{\fs40}Fuck you, man. I didn't ask for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.21,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我也没想问你\N{\fs40}You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.46,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这事没什么好结果 泰丝\N{\fs40}This isn't gonna end well, Tess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.08,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们得往回走\N{\fs40}We need to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.51,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,让我们把这票干完\N{\fs40}Let's just finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.85,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,她是否真如火萤所说 那不重要\N{\fs40}It doesn't matter if she is or she isn't what the Fireflies say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.93,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,只要他们坚信她是\N{\fs40}If they believe that she is then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.44,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们就可以得到我们想要的\N{\fs40}we get what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:52.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,如果她抽搐起来\N{\fs40}If she so much as twitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.78,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,别这么做\N{\fs40}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.70,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs40}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.42,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行吗？\N{\fs40}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.80,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\fs40}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.18,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,能给我把枪吗？\N{\fs40}Can I have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.48,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,- 绝对不行 - 不可以\N{\fs40}-Absolutely not. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.52,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行吧 老天 我朝他们扔他妈的三明治好了\N{\fs40}Okay, Jesus. Fine. I'll have to throw a fuckin' sandwich at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:44.33,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,外面安全\N{\fs40}It's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.00,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\fs40}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.36,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,哈 白天的外城看起来很不一样吧？\N{\fs40}Yeah, looks different in the daylight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:26.25,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们该走了\N{\fs40}We should get movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.01,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,看起来像是月球搞得一团糟的样子\N{\fs40}It's like a fucked-up moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.37,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这是被他们炸的？\N{\fs40}Is this where they bombed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.72,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.27,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,大多数大城市都被这么炸了\N{\fs40}They hit most of the big cities like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.40,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们得想办法阻止疫情蔓延\N{\fs40}They had to slow the spread somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:53.03,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这招在波士顿成功了 但在大多数地方都失败了\N{\fs40}Worked here, but it didn't in most places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.08,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,瞧 往前走就是州议会大厦\N{\fs40}So, the State House is across there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.79,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,如果直走 大概10分钟路程\N{\fs40}It's about a 10-minute walk if you could go straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:07.44,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那么？\N{\fs40}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.21,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,选远路还是近路？\N{\fs40}Long way or short way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:12.42,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,恐怕是选远路 还是选那条“我们他妈死定了”的路\N{\fs40}I mean, it's the long way or the "we're fuckin' dead" way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:16.05,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,考虑到这条含糊的信息 我给远路投一票\N{\fs40}Well, I vote long way just based on that limited information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们得先去酒店那看看\N{\fs40}We have to check it from the hotel first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.14,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs40}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.66,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那些玩意儿究竟在哪？\N{\fs40}Where the fuck are they already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.99,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,当他们靠近时 你会注意到的\N{\fs40}You'll know it when they're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,上次我就没发现\N{\fs40}I didn't know last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.37,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你怎么被咬的？\N{\fs40}How did you get bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.88,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,隔离区有个老购物中心 你听说过吗？\N{\fs40}You know the old mall in the QZ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.46,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你说的是上了锁 封了门\N{\fs40}The one that's sealed off and boarded up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.46,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,根本不让进的那个？\N{\fs40}and no one's supposed to go in, ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.67,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,就是那地方吗？\N{\fs40}That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.09,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,随便吧 反正我溜进去了\N{\fs40}Whatever. I snuck in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.93,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,想看看里边是什么样子\N{\fs40}Wanted to see what it was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.39,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,没想到那儿还有东西\N{\fs40}Didn't think there was gonna be anything in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.02,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,有个家伙不知从哪儿窜出来冲向我\N{\fs40}and then one just came at me outta nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我以为自己安全了 没想到\N{\fs40}Thought I got away, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.06,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你去的时候就你自己？\N{\fs40}So it was just you in there, alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:15.90,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs40}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.61,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你多大了？\N{\fs40}How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.24,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,十四岁\N{\fs40}Fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.24,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fs40}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.83,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我想说 你还挺有胆量的 小妹妹\N{\fs40}Well, I mean, you got some balls on you, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:27.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs40}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.14,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,没人来找你吧？\N{\fs40}Nobody's gonna be comin' after you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.39,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,比方说 你妈妈\N{\fs40}Like, Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.97,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fs40}Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.01,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,男朋友？\N{\fs40}boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.27,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我是个孤儿\N{\fs40}I'm an orphan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,而且 也没男朋友\N{\fs40}and, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.86,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,每个人都跟我说 外城很可怕\N{\fs40}Everyone said the open city was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,差不多就是 成群结队的感染者随处可见\N{\fs40}Like, swarms of Infected running around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.45,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不完全是那样\N{\fs40}Not exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.07,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,人们喜欢讲故事 你懂的\N{\fs40}You know, people like to tell stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:10.50,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,也就是说 没有什么超级感染者往你身上炸真菌孢子？\N{\fs40}So, there aren't Super-Infected that explode fungus spores on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.33,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,操 我倒希望不会有\N{\fs40}Shit, I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:16.42,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那 有没有脑袋裂开的那种？跟蝙蝠似的 在黑暗中也能看见\N{\fs40}Or ones with split-open heads that see in the dark like bats?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.68,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,什么声音？\N{\fs40}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.61,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,继续往前走吧\N{\fs40}Let's keep movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:15.44,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑！\N{\fs40}You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.27,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你俩曾经住过这地方？\N{\fs40}Ya ever stay in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.07,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不 这儿太高级了\N{\fs40}No, a little out of our league.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.51,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道这里是干嘛的？\N{\fs40}How do you even know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.92,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你难道没有听过书这种东西吗？\N{\fs40}Have you heard of books?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.20,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,等等 我们要下水？\N{\fs40}Wait, are we going in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.28,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,对 得去另一侧的楼梯井\N{\fs40}Yeah, we gotta get to the stairwell on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.29,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,呃 我不会游泳\N{\fs40}Well, I don't know how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:35.81,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,真的假的？\N{\fs40}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你觉得咱们那隔离区里会有游泳池？\N{\fs40}Do you think we have pools in the QZ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.17,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,聪明死你\N{\fs40}No, smart ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.17,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\fs40}I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.63,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能知道\N{\fs40}I don't know how I was supposed to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.73,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,太恶心了\N{\fs40}This is so gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.69,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,快来看！\N{\fs40}Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.91,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,叮 叮\N{\fs40}Ding, ding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:12.91,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,是的先生 我要你们最好的套房 谢谢\N{\fs40}Yes, sir. I would like your finest suite, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:15.20,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好的女士 需要我为您提行李吗？\N{\fs40}Yes, ma'am. Would you like me to take your luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.48,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好的女士 马上来 女士——\N{\fs40}Yes, ma'am. Right away, ma'am--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:18.50,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你真是个怪小孩\N{\fs40}You're a weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:20.46,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你才是怪小孩\N{\fs40}You're a weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.50,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我操！\N{\fs40}Oh fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.76,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs40}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:32.39,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs40}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:46.67,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\fs40}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:49.78,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,没事 好他妈极了\N{\fs40}Yep. Fucking fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:06.42,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,操 要人命了\N{\fs40}Fuck. Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:08.34,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,得了 没那么糟吧\N{\fs40}Come on, it wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:10.59,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你用我们的膝盖爬他妈十层试试\N{\fs40}You try climbing ten fuckin' floors with our knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.22,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,看看你啥感觉\N{\fs40}See how ya feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:24.90,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这他妈啥时候变这样了？\N{\fs40}Well, when the fuck did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:32.36,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,没准那扇能行\N{\fs40}Maybe that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:39.08,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行吧 我觉着 也许我可以爬上去\N{\fs40}All right, well, I mean, maybe I could climb up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:42.00,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,探探路 然后从里边开门？\N{\fs40}work my way around, and open it from the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:45.00,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,别 我个子最小 所以我爬过去最容易\N{\fs40}No, well, I'm the smallest, so it'd be easier for me to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:48.34,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你要死了我们就白忙活了 你留下来\N{\fs40}But you die and we get nothing. You stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:49.97,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,来帮我一把？\N{\fs40}Can you give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:11.15,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,上边没问题吧？\N{\fs40}You good up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:16.87,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,没问题 但有点乱 我可能需要几分钟\N{\fs40}Yeah, it's a bit of a mess, so I'm gonna need a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:49.52,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好刀\N{\fs40}Nice knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.91,0:24:56.09,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这招你哪儿学的？\N{\fs40}Where'd you learn to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.09,0:24:57.53,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,马戏团呀\N{\fs40}The circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:12.38,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你是哪里人？\N{\fs40}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.30,0:25:15.22,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,德克萨斯\N{\fs40}Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.34,0:25:17.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,泰丝呢？\N{\fs40}What about Tess?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.32,0:25:19.14,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,底特律 在密歇根州\N{\fs40}Detroit. It's in Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.22,0:25:21.89,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我上过学 我知道底特律在哪儿\N{\fs40}I go to school. I know where Detroit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.94,0:25:29.65,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,所以 你俩是——\N{\fs40}So, you two like a--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.73,0:25:30.52,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,过\N{\fs40}Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.78,0:25:33.09,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你是怎么到波士顿来的？\N{\fs40}How'd you end up in Boston?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.09,0:25:33.90,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,过\N{\fs40}Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.57,0:25:36.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,别再问我的事了\N{\fs40}No more questions about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:44.37,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,感染者能活多久？\N{\fs40}How long do Infected live?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.45,0:25:45.75,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我还以为你上过学呢\N{\fs40}I thought you went to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.83,0:25:47.92,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我那学校傻逼得很\N{\fs40}It's a really shitty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.54,0:25:53.09,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,有的能活一两个月\N{\fs40}Well, some last about a month or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.21,0:25:56.76,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,但也有游荡了20年左右的\N{\fs40}But there's others been walkin' around 'bout 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:02.33,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你杀过吗？\N{\fs40}Ever kill one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.52,0:26:04.31,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,嗯 我杀过很多\N{\fs40}Yeah, I killed lots of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.40,0:26:10.52,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,难下手吗？\N{\fs40}Was it hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.36,0:26:13.69,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,毕竟 你会想 他们曾经是人\N{\fs40}Like, knowing they were people once?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:18.74,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,有时候吧\N{\fs40}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.70,0:26:23.24,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,昨晚那个人呢？\N{\fs40}What about that guy last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.46,0:26:31.04,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,把枪放下 乔尔\N{\fs40}Put the gun down, Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.68,0:26:42.22,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办？\N{\fs40}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.85,0:27:29.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,居然这么多\N{\fs40}There's so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.73,0:27:32.44,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,上次我们来这儿 它们还在大楼内部深处\N{\fs40}The last time we were here, they were still deep inside the buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.52,0:27:35.07,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我猜后来跑来找隔离区的人太多了\N{\fs40}Then I guess enough people came through looking for the QZ,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.15,0:27:37.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们进到大楼里 找地方躲着\N{\fs40}they went inside seeking shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.40,0:27:41.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,于是感染者一点一点 一年一年地蚕食掉这座城市\N{\fs40}and that's how they get more and more of the city bit by bit, year after year.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.33,0:27:53.88,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,它们彼此相连\N{\fs40}They're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.67,0:27:56.21,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,程度比你以为得更紧密\N{\fs40}More than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.84,0:27:59.09,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,真菌也生长在地下\N{\fs40}The fungus also grows underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.17,0:28:02.88,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,像电线一样长的纤维 有的能延伸到一英里外\N{\fs40}Long fibers like wires, some of them stretching over a mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.97,0:28:05.80,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你要是踩到了一个地方的线虫草菌\N{\fs40}Now, you step on a patch of cordyceps in one place,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.89,0:28:09.52,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,也许就能唤醒别处十几个感染者\N{\fs40}and you can wake a dozen Infected from somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.14,0:28:12.69,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,它们知道了你的位置 就都过来了\N{\fs40}Now they know where you are, now they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.77,0:28:16.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你的免疫能力可挡不住他们把你大卸八块\N{\fs40}You're not immune from being ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.98,0:28:18.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？\N{\fs40}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:21.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这很重要\N{\fs40}It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.99,0:28:23.53,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我在教你保命\N{\fs40}I'm tryin' to keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.95,0:28:32.50,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,所以我们不走那边\N{\fs40}So we're not goin' that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.79,0:28:34.71,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.46,0:28:37.79,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那我们怎么办？\N{\fs40}What do we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.00,0:28:40.63,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,走近路？\N{\fs40}Short way?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.43,0:28:45.55,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,走博物馆\N{\fs40}Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.87,0:29:08.99,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你他妈是在开玩笑吧\N{\fs40}You've gotta be fucking kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.74,0:29:12.20,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,楼顶有条路能过去\N{\fs40}Well, there's a way across from the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.29,0:29:13.71,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好啊 你们说行就行\N{\fs40}Well, then I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.79,0:29:14.94,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这条路我们常走\N{\fs40}We used to take it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.94,0:29:16.00,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs40}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.08,0:29:17.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,听着 这路没问题\N{\fs40}Look, it was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.11,0:29:18.50,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fs40}Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.55,0:29:30.89,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,干透了\N{\fs40}It's bone dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.60,0:29:33.93,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,可能里边的都死光了\N{\fs40}It could mean they're all finally dead in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:40.77,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\fs40}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.73,0:29:44.07,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,玛琳给你带了这个吗\N{\fs40}Marlene pack you one of these
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.15,0:29:45.38,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,还是只装了三明治？\N{\fs40}or just sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.38,0:29:45.80,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,带了\N{\fs40}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.53,0:29:49.95,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好了 还有几条规矩\N{\fs40}Okay, so, more ground rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.03,0:29:51.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们动作要慢\N{\fs40}We're gonna go slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.70,0:29:53.37,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,如果我们遇着了什么东西 你躲在我们身后\N{\fs40}If we come up against anything, you get behind us
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.45,0:29:55.16,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,在原地待好 行吗？\N{\fs40}and ya stay there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.25,0:29:56.16,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,知道了\N{\fs40}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.00,0:30:02.34,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我空出来了一只手\N{\fs40}I have a spare hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.84,0:30:04.38,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,恭喜你啊\N{\fs40}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.81,0:31:01.10,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,没错 死透了\N{\fs40}Yeah, cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.15,0:31:03.69,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,总算有点狗屎运\N{\fs40}Finally, some fuckin' luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.15,0:31:07.07,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,早知道我们一开始就走这边了\N{\fs40}I guess we should've gone this way in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.53,0:31:09.78,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我操！\N{\fs40}Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.37,0:31:16.91,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这他妈什么东西干的？\N{\fs40}What the fuck did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.04,0:31:23.59,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,可能\N{\fs40}Maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.00,0:31:28.34,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,可能他在外面受的袭击 然后爬进门里\N{\fs40}maybe he was attacked outside, and crawled through the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.42,0:31:30.97,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,门是开的 也许就是他\N{\fs40}The door was open. Could've been him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.30,0:31:33.24,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我什么都没听到\N{\fs40}I don't hear anything. 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.24,0:31:34.85,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,会听到什么？\N{\fs40}Who would you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.51,0:31:38.73,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,会听到什么？\N{\fs40}Who would you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.81,0:31:40.98,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你是说这是感染者干的？\N{\fs40}Are you saying an Infected did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.94,0:31:44.94,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我被感染者袭击过 但不是这样的\N{\fs40}Because I've been attacked by one and it wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.98,0:31:51.07,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好了 从现在开始 我们要完全无声\N{\fs40}Okay, from this point forward, we are silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.15,0:31:53.24,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不是安静 完全无声\N{\fs40}Not quiet. Silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.32,0:31:54.01,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,什么—— \N{\fs40}What--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.01,0:31:57.08,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,别 别问问题 只管照做\N{\fs40}No. No questions. Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.91,0:35:31.54,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,它们看不见 但能听到\N{\fs40}They can't see, but they can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.49,0:36:08.74,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,快跑！\N{\fs40}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.09,0:36:26.39,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,跑 快跑！\N{\fs40}Run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.68,0:39:10.49,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\fs40}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.49,0:39:14.01,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,脚踝扭了 但问题不大\N{\fs40}Twisted ankle, but, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.27,0:39:18.68,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\fs40}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.77,0:39:21.31,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我没尿裤子 所以 还行\N{\fs40}Well, I didn't shit my pants, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.19,0:39:26.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这他妈逗我吗？\N{\fs40}You fucking kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.94,0:39:30.86,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,如果咱仨里非得有个人被咬 那就这样吧\N{\fs40}I mean, if it was gonna happen to one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.53,0:39:34.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs40}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.70,0:39:36.45,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,咱快他妈离开这儿吧\N{\fs40}let's get the fuck outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.18,0:39:56.54,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,缠你胳膊上\N{\fs40}Put this around your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.54,0:39:57.31,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs40}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.68,0:40:01.46,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,走过去？\N{\fs40}Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.46,0:40:03.27,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,对的 我知道 看着挺吓人\N{\fs40}Yeah, I know. It looks scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.35,0:40:06.27,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,刚刚才叫吓人 这是块木板而已\N{\fs40}That was scary. This is wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.15,0:40:11.70,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,在那儿等着 等我们一会儿\N{\fs40}Just wait there. Give us a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.71,0:40:24.46,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,前边估计还有更多\N{\fs40}There's probably more ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.63,0:40:27.17,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那我们到时候再处理\N{\fs40}So, we'll deal with it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.13,0:40:29.88,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我来吧 我来\N{\fs40}I got it. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.84,0:40:35.55,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那小孩怎么办？\N{\fs40}What about the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.64,0:40:37.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我是说 也许第一次被咬没感染\N{\fs40}I mean, maybe the first bite didn't take,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.72,0:40:38.70,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那这第二次呢？\N{\fs40}but what about the second?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.70,0:40:40.31,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你就不能看着点好？\N{\fs40}How 'bout you just take the good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.64,0:40:42.77,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行吗？\N{\fs40}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:46.40,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这次你就不能好好想想 我们或许真有机会成功？\N{\fs40}Like to think, for once, maybe we could actually win?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.52,0:40:50.44,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,过去吧 过去看着她\N{\fs40}Just go, go and watch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.34,0:41:16.89,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这一切都如你所愿吗？\N{\fs40}Is it everything you hoped for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.18,0:41:19.72,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,还不好说\N{\fs40}Jury's still out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.93,0:41:24.48,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,但老兄 这景色绝了\N{\fs40}But, man, you can't deny that view.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.28,0:41:33.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,来吧 咱得在天黑之前到\N{\fs40}C'mon, let's get there before it's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.90,0:42:53.02,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们他妈在哪儿呢？\N{\fs40}Where the fuck are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.94,0:43:35.07,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,待着别动\N{\fs40}Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.81,0:44:08.35,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,乔尔？\N{\fs40}Joel?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.10,0:44:10.33,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这他妈怎么回事？\N{\fs40}What the fuck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.79,0:44:11.35,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs40}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.44,0:44:18.40,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们进去了\N{\fs40}They went inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.20,0:44:24.37,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 - 泰丝\N{\fs40}-Come on. -Tess.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.45,0:44:25.53,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,来吧！\N{\fs40}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.62,0:44:26.74,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,泰丝！\N{\fs40}Tess!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.17,0:44:39.71,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我操\N{\fs40}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.30,0:44:43.47,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs40}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.06,0:44:54.06,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs40}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.14,0:44:58.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我说 这儿肯定有他妈的收音机之类的 对吧？\N{\fs40}I mean, there's gotta be a fuckin' radio or somethin', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.90,0:45:02.65,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,谁杀了他们？FEDRA的人？\N{\fs40}Who killed them? FEDRA?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.86,0:45:04.78,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不对\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.24,0:45:08.87,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们当中有人被咬了\N{\fs40}One of them got bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.95,0:45:10.91,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,健康的跟病了的打了起来 所有人都输了\N{\fs40}The healthy ones fought the sick ones. Everyone lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.99,0:45:13.54,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,泰丝？你在干嘛？\N{\fs40}Tess? What're you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.08,0:45:16.71,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,玛琳说要带你到哪儿去？\N{\fs40}Where did Marlene say that she was taking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.79,0:45:17.36,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,艾莉！\N{\fs40}Ellie!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.36,0:45:19.25,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我不知道 只说在西边\N{\fs40}I don't know. Just west.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.34,0:45:20.92,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,就是西边 他妈的 行吧\N{\fs40}Just west. Fuck. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.00,0:45:24.88,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,行 我是说 他们中间肯定有人身上有地图 对吧？\N{\fs40}Well, I mean, one of them's gotta have a map on them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.97,0:45:26.03,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,乔尔 你能帮把手吗？\N{\fs40}Joel, can ya help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.03,0:45:27.09,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不能！\N{\fs40}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.18,0:45:29.76,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,泰丝 结束了\N{\fs40}Tess, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.85,0:45:31.29,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们现在回家\N{\fs40}We are going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.29,0:45:33.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,那他妈不是我的家！\N{\fs40}That's not my fucking home!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.07,0:45:49.62,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我要留下来\N{\fs40}I'm stayin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.08,0:45:55.12,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我是说 我们的好运迟早会用完\N{\fs40}I mean, our luck had to run out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.62,0:45:58.17,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fs40}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.13,0:46:00.67,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,她被感染了\N{\fs40}She's infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.84,0:46:09.97,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,让我看一下\N{\fs40}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.89,0:46:13.02,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,乔尔\N{\fs40}Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.40,0:46:28.16,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,真惨 对吧？\N{\fs40}Oops, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.87,0:46:37.79,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,把你的绷带取下来\N{\fs40}Take your bandage off.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.34,0:46:44.46,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,乔尔\N{\fs40}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.13,0:46:46.26,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,看见了么？\N{\fs40}Joel?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.18,0:46:49.55,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这是真的\N{\fs40}This is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.64,0:46:51.64,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,乔尔 她是真他妈的免疫\N{\fs40}Joel, she's fucking real.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.97,0:46:56.56,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我要你把她送到比尔和弗兰克那儿去\N{\fs40}I need you to get her to Bill and Frank's.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.64,0:46:58.10,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,- 不行 - 他们会从你那儿接手她\N{\fs40}-No. -They'll take her off your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.19,0:46:59.48,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,- 不行 - 之后他们来操心\N{\fs40}-No. -They'll handle it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.56,0:47:00.77,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不行 他们不会接手的\N{\fs40}No, no, no, I can't. They won't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.85,0:47:01.75,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们不会接收她的\N{\fs40}They're not gonna take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.75,0:47:03.11,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,他们会 因为你会说服他们\N{\fs40}They will 'cause you'll convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.19,0:47:04.32,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你会的\N{\fs40}Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.40,0:47:06.24,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我从没有要求过你什么\N{\fs40}I never ask you for anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.32,0:47:07.86,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,- 没要你回馈感情 - 不行\N{\fs40}-not to feel the way I felt. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.95,0:47:09.70,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,把嘴他妈闭上 因为我没时间了\N{\fs40}Shut the fuck up 'cause I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.32,0:47:11.87,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,这是你的机会\N{\fs40}This is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.87,0:47:14.41,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你送她过去\N{\fs40}You get her there,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.12,0:47:16.66,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你保她活命\N{\fs40}you keep her alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.66,0:47:20.58,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你就能重回正道\N{\fs40}and you set everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.59,0:47:25.05,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们可是做过了那么多破事\N{\fs40}All the shit we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.00,0:47:27.92,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,拜托你答应 乔尔 求你了\N{\fs40}Please say yes, Joel, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.80,0:47:29.93,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我操！\N{\fs40}Oh fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.60,0:48:20.37,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,有多少？\N{\fs40}How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.37,0:48:21.02,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,全都来了\N{\fs40}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.10,0:48:22.10,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,顶多一分钟到\N{\fs40}Maybe a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.41,0:48:36.39,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\N{\fs40}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.39,0:48:38.08,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,确保他们追不上你们\N{\fs40}Making sure that they don't follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.92,0:48:53.05,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,乔尔\N{\fs40}Joel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.01,0:48:58.93,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,救你能救的人\N{\fs40}Save who you can save.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.52,0:49:08.44,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs40}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.98,0:49:10.98,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我们不能丢下她！\N{\fs40}We're not leaving her!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.07,0:49:12.74,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,放开我 你个混蛋！\N{\fs40}Get off me, you fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.82,0:49:14.28,Subtitle-TLOU,,0,0,0,,我不要跟你走！\N{\fs40}I'm not going with you!
